===關島===
7月10日，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局天气预报办公室]]基于[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]的公告，与NWS关岛联合发布了热带风暴警告，这个警报的对象是[[关岛|关岛]]、[[天宁岛|天宁岛]]、[[羅塔島|罗塔岛]]、[[塞班岛|塞班岛]]以及关岛周围海域约75公里的区域<ref name="Guam 1" /><ref name="Guam 1">{{cite web|archivedate=2014-07-11|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|work=Weather Forecast Office in Tiyan, Guam|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/data/GUM/TCPPQ1|title=Tropical Depression 09W Advisory Number 1, July 10, 2014 15z|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QywYeMUC?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ32-PGUM_201407101600.htm|accessdate=2014-07-19|date=2014-07-10|author=Williams, Derek L}}</ref>。随后，关岛总督Eddie Calvo宣布，关岛地区发布3号热带气旋警告以及烈风警报，预计强风将达到80-95km/h(50-60节）<ref>{{cite news|date=2014-07-10|agency=Kuam News|title=Governor declares Condition of Readiness 3|url=http://www.kuam.com/story/25991947/2014/07/10/governor-declares-condition-of-readiness-3|author=Matanane, Sabrina Salas|accessdate=2014-07-13}}</ref>。这两个警报意味着烈风将会在48小时内袭击警戒地区<ref name="Guam 1"/>。随后，威马逊被联合台风警报中心升格为热带风暴，而关岛地区亦将警报提升为二级<ref>{{cite web|work=Weather Forecast Office in Tiyan, Guam|archivedate=2014-07-11|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|author=Ziobro, Michael P|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/data/GUM/TCPPQ1|title=Tropical Storm 09W Advisory Number 3, July 11, 2014 03z|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QywX7BCY?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ32-PGUM_201407110307.htm|accessdate=2014-07-19|date=2014-07-11}}</ref><ref name="Depression-Storm">{{cite news|date=July 11, 2014|title=Depression 09W Now a Tropical Storm|agency=Kuam News|author=Matanane, Sabrina Salas|url=http://www.kuam.com/story/25992818/2014/07/10/depression-09w-now-a-tropical-storm|accessdate=2014-07-19}}</ref><ref name="TCCOR 2">{{cite news|date=July 11, 2014|title=Guam now in Condition of Readiness 2|url=http://www.kuam.com/story/25992260/2014/07/10/guam-now-in-condition-of-readiness-2|agency=Kuam News|accessdate=2014-07-19|author=Matanane, Sabrina Salas}}</ref>。此时，除了政府及必要企业，其他司法机关及企业被强制关闭<ref name="Depression-Storm"/><ref name="TCCOR 2"/><ref>{{cite news|title=Closures announced for storm|date=2014-07-11|url=http://www.kuam.com/story/25992528/2014/07/10/closures-announced-for-storm|agency=Kuam News|accessdate=2014-07-19|author=Matanane, Sabrina Salas}}</ref><ref name="hit Guam">{{cite news|title=Storm to hit Guam: Governor declares Condition of Readiness 1|date=2014-07-12|url=http://www.guampdn.com/article/20140712/NEWS01/307120008/Storm-hit-Guam-Governor-declares-Condition-Readiness-1|agency=Pacific Daily News|accessdate=2014-07-19|archive-date=2014-07-26|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140726221648/http://www.guampdn.com/article/20140712/NEWS01/307120008/Storm-hit-Guam-Governor-declares-Condition-Readiness-1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，岛上6所小学被作为庇护所，而38周以上孕妇及其他高风险人群将被紧急安置在关岛纪念医院<ref name="Depression-Storm"/>。

7月11日傍晚，一号警告被发出，禁止一切户外活动<ref name="hit Guam"/>。

7月12日清晨，关岛地区取消一切警报。此时威马逊被联合台风警报中心降格为热带低气压<ref>{{cite web|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|archivedate=2014-07-12|work=Weather Forecast Office in Tiyan, Guam|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/data/GUM/TCPPQ1|title=Tropical Depression 09W Advisory Number 6, July 11, 2014 21z|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6R0NNEIhb?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ32-PGUM_201407112132.htm|accessdate=2014-07-19|date=2014-07-11|author=Middlebrooke, Michael G}}</ref><ref name="TSWC">{{cite news|date=2014-07-12|title=Tropical Storm Warning canceled for Guam & Rota|url=http://www.kuam.com/story/25999528/2014/07/11/tropical-storm-warning-could-be-called-off-at-8am|publisher=Kuam News|accessdate=2014-07-19|author=Matanane, Sabrina Salas}}</ref>。总督Eddie Calvo重新恢复关岛的季节性警报<ref name="TCCOR 4">{{cite news|date=2014-07-12|title=Governor declares Condition of Readiness 4, tropical storm warning canceled|url=http://www.guampdn.com/article/20140712/NEWS01/140711001/Governor-declares-Condition-Readiness-4-tropical-storm-warning-canceled|agency=Pacific Daily News|accessdate=2014-07-19|archive-date=2014-07-20|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140720182629/http://www.guampdn.com/article/20140712/NEWS01/140711001/Governor-declares-Condition-Readiness-4-tropical-storm-warning-canceled|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。NWC关岛随后指出，威马逊并未在关岛地区登陆，而是通过罗塔海峡。这么一来，风雨对关岛的影响会比预期略弱，并且没有如预期对关岛地区产生破坏性的烈风<ref name="AFD 12/7/14"/>。

